casebody.data:
New York Juvenile Asylum, Respondent, v. Cane, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. June 26, 1890.) Appeal from eighth district court.

Argued before Allen, P. J., and Bookstaver, J.

L. Mathot, for appellant. Dixon, Williams & Ashley, for respondent.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with costs.
